title: Jordan Dreyer from La Dispute
itunes:title: Jordan Dreyer from La Dispute
description:
In an extremely special show, I speak with Jordan Dreyer the vocalist for La Dispute. We openly discuss acting, the process of being creative and unintentional beginnings. For a man with very little social media presence, he was very candid and open in our talk.
